c: 59
v: 9
t: "Naho babandi batuye mbere yabo iki gihugu (cya Madina), bahisemo ukwemera banakunda abimutse babagana, kandi mu mitima ntibararikire ibyo (abo bimukira) bahawe, ahubwo bagaharira abandi bo biretse, kabone n’ubwo nabo ubwabo bagaba babikeneye. Kandi abarinzwe kugira ubugugu ni bo bazatsinda"